items.title: Nvidia rides AI wave to pass Apple as world’s largest company
items.description: Nvidia accounts for 7% of the weight of the S&P 500 Index and is responsible for about a quarter of the benchmark’s 21% gain this year.

items.title: Titan Company: Second half of FY25 likely to be stronger

items.title: HZL OFS over-subscribed by institutional investors; attracts Rs 3,400-crore worth bids
